Program: Outlook
Title: Heading forensic psychiatry in Uganda
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0104hxb
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 6 Nov 2012
Dr Margaret Mungherera, a forensic psychiatrist from Uganda, tells how she's become friends with one of the killers she treated. Zhu Shumei is the basketball playing granny from China who's become an internet hit. And Massoud Hassani is the Afghan-born man who's designed a wind powered mine sweeper based on his childhood toys. Image: Dr Margaret Mungherera Show less